description:
Available in: English, German. Moon Info Pro delivers a lot of information about the moon. It provides exact calculations of moon phases and lunar details on WebOS over a period stretching from 1900 to 2100. All times are shown in relation to the given time-zone and to Daylight Savings Time

FEATURES:
+ moon phase
+ moon-rise and moon-set
+ sun-rise, sun-set, dawn & dusk (blue hour for photographers)
+ illumination in percent
+ age of the moon within a moon cycle
+ distance in kilometres and miles
+ number of lunation
+ signs of the zodiac
+ constellation
+ coordinates (ecliptical, geocentric / topocentric, altitude & azimuth)
+ passing moon through the nodes
+ apogee / perigee
+ Some astrological infos (Moon Void of Course, moon ascending/descending, element)

*** V1.1.2 - VOC-Data for 2011 added!  ***   

The Void of Course data in this version are for 2010 and 2011, further data will follow in an update.
